 6.2 SSL Certificate Scanner

This module establishes a secure connection with target domains and retrieves certificate metadata.

Extracted Information:

* Domain Name
* Certificate Issuer
* Valid From Date
* Expiry Date
* Serial Number

 Process

1. Connect to domain on port 443.
2. Perform SSL handshake.
3. Retrieve certificate.
4. Extract metadata.
5. Calculate expiry details.



 6.3 Risk Classification Module

The system classifies certificates based on the number of days remaining.

| Days Remaining | Status   |
| -------------- | -------- |
| ≤ 7 Days       | Critical |
| ≤ 30 Days      | Warning  |
| > 30 Days      | Healthy  |

This classification helps administrators prioritize certificate renewals.

