 7. Workflow

1. User enters a domain.
2. SSL Scanner retrieves certificate details.
3. Expiry information is extracted.
4. Remaining validity is calculated.
5. Risk level is determined.
6. AI Agent generates recommendations.
7. Results are stored in SQLite.
8. Dashboard updates analytics.
9. Reports can be exported.



